        <Parent_String>oil varnish [300014989], varnish by composition [300014987], varnish [300014974], coating by composition or origin [300014908], coating (material) [300014907], materials by function [300014692], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
